    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox and a variable M Differential Lock. This specimen has received proactive maintenance on critical areas, including a reinforced rear subframe and a serviced VANOS system to ensure precise camshaft timing. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance the E46 chassis is renowned for. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal acquisition for the purist seeking a visceral, naturally aspirated performance experience.",
